official_title: Resolution authorizing additional printing of the report entitled "Executive Orders in Times of War and National Emergency".

summary.text: Authorizes the printing of 1,700 additional copies of the report entitled "Executive Orders in Times of War and National Emergency" for the use of the Special Committee on National Emergencies and Delegated Emergency Powers.
